	<text>
		<body xml:lang="en">
			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_001230_0001"/><!--pb/@n='1r'-->
<lb/><p rend="center"><space extent="1" unit="chars"/><placeName>18. Hart St.</placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="center"><space extent="2" unit="chars"/>13 Feby </p>
<lb/><p rend="center"><space extent="3" unit="chars"/>1858 </p>
<lb/>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">Dear <persName>Captain Washington</persName></p>
<lb/><p>I have just 
<lb/>come in from 
<lb/>an interview 
<lb/>with <persName>her Majesty</persName>
<lb/>or I should 
<lb/>have answered 
<lb/>yours before this<reg>.</reg>

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_001230_0002"/><!--pb/@n='1v'--> 
<lb/>I got two 
<lb/>estimates from 
<lb/>the city through 
<lb/><persName>Sir Morton 
<lb/>Peto</persName> but they 
<lb/>were an 
<lb/>increase in 
<lb/>amount of 
<lb/>food and 
<lb/>a <unclear cert="medium">proportionable</unclear>
<lb/>increase in 

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_001230_0003"/><!--pb/@n='2r'--> 
<lb/>Price - one 
<lb/>was £750 
<lb/>another £1003 
<lb/>So there can 
<lb/>be no doubt 
<lb/>but <persName>Duncan's</persName>
<lb/>man is 
<lb/>reasonable<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>It will be well 
<lb/>to decide to 
<lb/>get them from 

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_001230_0004"/><!--pb/@n='2v'--> 
<lb/>Glasgow - I 
<lb/>shall want 
<lb/>a day or two - 
<lb/>We sent down 
<lb/>our two 
<lb/>years luggage 
<lb/>to <placeName>Liverpool</placeName>
<lb/>today<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p>Hoping this 
<lb/>is in time 
<lb/>for post<reg>.</reg> I am &amp;c </p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><persName>David Livingstone</persName></p>
			
</div>
